owltools.mooncat.ontologymetadata
Class ImportChainDotWriter

java.lang.Object
  owltools.mooncat.ontologymetadata.ImportChainDotWriter

public class ImportChainDotWriter
extends Object

Rudimentary implementation of a DOT writer for the LEGO annotations in OWL. Uses the 'docs/lego-owl-mappings.txt' file as guide-line.
